data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!! Priced to sell! This four bedroom, 2.5 bath craftsman style home is ready for immediate move-in. Sitting on a corner lot at the front of the neighborhood, enjoy a fully wooden fenced-in level backyard and rocking chair front porch. Upon entering the front door, you have a study to your right and a dining room to your left. Directly behind the dining is an eat-in kitchen with black appliances, plus bar seating. Moving past the stone fireplace living room is the stairwell to all of your beds and baths. Your master has trey ceilings and a sliding barn door into the double vanity master bath, complete with a soaking tub, updated tile shower with glass door, and an entrance to the laundry room. All of this in a quiet neighborhood minutes from downtown Statham!   Make an appointment today and let's put your LAST name on this FRONT door!
